                     <h3 class="content">April 23, 2005</h3>
                     <a id="a000115"></a>
                     <div class="content" id="entry-115">
                        <h3 class="content">good friends and good parking meters</h3>
                        <div class="content">
                           <div class="content">
                              <p><a href="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/mt3.14/johannab/archives/parkingmeter-sandiego.html" onclick="window.open('http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/mt3.14/johannab/archives/parkingmeter-sandiego.html','popup','width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0'); return false"><br />
<img src="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/mt3.14/johannab/archives/parkingmeter-sandiego.jpg" width="160" height="120"></a></p>

<p>two travelling greeks stopped by orange county on their whirlwind tour around the west coast during my dark age [time spent sans computer].  they were a breath of fresh urban air, and we took our bad selves down to san diego for a day.  we went to a coffee shop you could smoke in, walked in pedestrian areas, went to little italy [which was a bit more mexican than italian, but still, the restaurant we ate in was perfect good ole fashioned italian-american], and walked back along the water front.  most importantly tho, seconds are not displayed ;]</p>
                              
                              <p class="posted">
                                 <span class="post-footers">roxy said on 01:54 AM</span> <span class="separator">|</span> <a class="permalink" href="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/blogs/setbang/2005/04/good_friends_and_good_parking.html">Permalink</a>
                                 | <a href="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/blogs/setbang/2005/04/good_friends_and_good_parking.html#comments">Comments (0)</a>
                                 
                              </p>
                           </div>
