                     <div class="content" id="entry-90">
                        <h3 class="content">chi 2005</h3>
                        <div class="content">
                           <div class="content">
                              <p><a href="http://www.inf.ethz.ch/personal/coroama/">vlad</a> asked me to submit something to his <a href="http://www.chi2005.org/">chi 2005</a> workshop <a href="http://www.vs.inf.ethz.ch/events/ubisoc2005/">ubisoc</a> on social implications of ubiquitous computing.  i did just that, and my <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~johannab/papers/JohannaBrewer-CHI2005-UbiSoc-Paper.pdf">paper</a> was accepted.  i will be off to portland then at the beginning of april along with pretty much everyone else from my department.  we will bring the funk.</p>
                              
